## What is SvelteKit
Building an **app** with all the modern best practices is fiendishly complicated. Those practices include ***build*** optimizations # Getting started This is a section of some simple filler text, also known as placeholder text. It shares some characteristics of a real written text but is random or otherwise generated. It may be used to display a sample of fonts or generate text for testing. Filler text is dummy text which has no meaning however looks very similar to real text. The important factor when using filler text is that the text looks realistic otherwise it will not look very good.
